  <answer><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You can add a ski carriage at time of booking. Booking in advance will help you secure the best possible price. On some flights, ski carriage is limited so we recommend booking as soon as possible.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you are travelling on one of our Jet2 charter flights, you can book ski carriage directly with Jet2 <a rel="noopener" href="https://reservations.jet2.com/Jet2.Reservations.Web.Portal/whitelabellandingpage.aspx?j2tid=520d181a-b94b-484a-a685-78b41b052e62?j2tid=93e4b75e-fae1-4048-9f3f-aa805912fcbc" target="_blank" data-anchor="?j2tid=93e4b75e-fae1-4048-9f3f-aa805912fcbc">via their website</a>. You will be asked for your Inghams reference number so make sure you have this to hand before booking.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It’s important to note that ski carriage will be slightly more expensive when booking via Jet2 and it can only be done 7 days after your booking is confirmed by Inghams.<br /></span></p>
<p> </p>]]></answer>
